Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.collection

Interface DateTimeComparable

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable, Equatable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DateCollection, DateTimeCollection
public interface DateTimeComparable extends Comparable
An interface indicating that a class can be compared as a DateTime.

This includes both DateTime and Date, as per the FHIRPath specification. Also includes Instant, which has to be specified at least up to seconds precision so should be comparable with DateTime of the same precision.

Author:
Piotr Szul
